29 Gdm02.026 ka 306a4-313b2 chos thams cad byang chub kyi sems rdzogs pa chen po 'khor ba rtsad nad gcod pa rin po che dang mnyam pa skye ba med pa'i rgyud sarba d+harmaH ma hA san+d+hi bo d+hi tsit+ta saM sa ra mu la ts+tshe da ma ha rat+na sa man+ta a bud pa to tan+t+ra rdzogs so// //rgya gar gyi mkhhan po shrI sing ha dang/ bos kyi lo ts+tsha bai ro tsa nas bsgyur ba'o// /snga 'gyur lnga dang phyi 'gyur bcu gsum gyi rgyud la rnyi ba'i ban chung nyi ma rdo rjes byas pa
66 Gdm02.027 ka 313b2-337b7 ye shes gsang ba zhes bya ba'i rgyud dz+nyA na gu h+ya nA ma tan+t+ra rdzogs s+ho// //san+d+hi ma hA gu h+ya na ma tan+t+ra/ rgya gar gyi mkhan po shrI sing ha fang/ bod kyi lo ts+tsha ba pa gor bai ro tsa nas/ yul d+ha he na'i 'dus khang du sgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o
67 Gdm02.028 ka 337b7-348b5 byang chub kyi sems ye shes rdzogs pa'i rgyud ces bya ba bo d+hi tsit+ta a ti dz+nyA na san+d+hi tan+t+ra nA ma rdzogs so// //rgya gar gyi mkhan po shrI sing+ha sang/ bod kyi lo ts+tsha ba bai ro tsa nas d+ha he na'i 'du khang du bsgyur ba'o
64 Gdm02.029 ka 348b5-359b1 ye shes gsang ba sgron ma rin po che man ngag gi rgyud ces bya ba dz+nyA na gu h+ya ri bu ma rat+na u pa de sha tan+t+ra bA ma ye shes gsang ba sgron ma rin po che'i rgyud ces bya ba rdzogs so// //paN Ti ta shri sing+ha dang/ zhu chen gyi lo ts+tsha ba bai ro tsa nas man ngag gi rgyud gtan la phab pa'o
62 Gdm02.030 ka 359b1-370a6 rin po che 'phags lam bkod pa'i rgyud ces bya ba rat+na A r+ya pa tha da ri tan+t+ra nA ma rin po che 'phags lam bkod pa'i rgyud ces bya ba rdzogs so// rgya gar gyi mkhan po paN+Di ta shrI sing ha dang/ bod kyi lo tsa ba chen po bai ro tsa nas bsgyur cing gtan la phab pa'o

48 Gdm03.009 kha 270b7-287a3 byang chub kyi sems rmad du byung ba'i rgyud bo d+hi tsit+ta ra tsa nu ha tan+t+ra rdzogs s+ho// //byang chub kyi sems rmad du byung ba' phyi ma ta ma nyid dang gsum bzhugs pa las/ zab mo bu ti'i lha khang du bu gnyis lus so/ /slob dpon bu d+d+ha kup+tas snums bar bzhengs nas/ lan gcig gzigs pas/ gnod sbyin kha rtsal gyi 'graxxx du thal lcag gcig rgyab nas brgyal bar gyur to/ brgyal sangs pa dang/ srin po lta bu'i tshul du 'dug pas smras pa/ gnas khang rgyal par gyur pa 'di nyid lyo rgyal po ,e 'od khyod kyi me khyer ro/ /gal te khyer na khyod nyid bsad par bya/ zhes smras pas/ bred nas dngangs nas/ ma ni gong du spyan gzhan zhig tu drangs/ bu gnyis der lus so/ /gang de nyid rnam par 'grel ba la/ /dgos don gsal 'tshad don la 'char ba ni/ /ma bu gsum nas drangs nas gtan la phab/ /phyi nas blo'i zer las skyod nas bya bzod na/ 'phags thugs 'gal dang 'phral du gnod sbyin mos/ /bar chad byed phyir blo'i gzer la skyod/ /las stod mkhas pa mgon po la/ myang stod lce nag bdud rstis zhus

rdzogs s+ho//

182 Gdm04.010 ga 141b1-142b5 ye shes sa gcig chos kyi dbyings dz+nyA d+harma e d+harma d+hA tu rdzogs so// //rgya gar gyi mkhas pa shrI sing+ha dang/ bod kyi lo ts+tsha ba bai ro tsa nas bsgyur pa'o

406 Gdm04.024 ga 266b5-275b3 chos thams cad byang chub kyi sems rdzogs pa chen po 'khor ba rtsad nas gcod pa nam mkha' dang mnyam pa ye shes 'od kyi rgyud sarba d+harma ma hA san d+hi bo d+hi tsit+ta saM sA ra mU la tshe da ma hA A kA sha sa man+ta dz+nyA na pra b+ha tan+t+ra nam mkha' dang myanm pa ye shes 'od kyi rgyud rdzogs so
196 Gdm04.025 ga 275b3-347b4 chos thams cad rdzogs pa chen po nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud chen po zhes bya ba sarba d+harma san ta k+Sha pa rA na tan tra ma hA na ma ma hA a ti yo ga g+hu h+ya pra de sha/ kha sa man ta na ma kha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud rdzogs so// //rgya gar gyi mkhan po dpal seng ge'i 'od can gyi zhal lda nas dang/ zhu chen gyi lots+tsha ba dge slong gan jag rnam par snang mdzad kyi zhal gzigs pa des/ yul d+ha he na'i 'du khang du/ bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o
197 Gdm04.026 ga 347b4-369a6 byang chub kyi sems nam mkha' rgya mtsho rdzogs pa chen po gsang ba rgyud kyi rgyal po zhes bya ba bo d+hi tsit+ta kha ma se ta a kam ka ra san ti ma hA gu h+ya tan tra ra dza nA ma byang chub kyi sems/ rdzogs pa chen po/ klong chen rab 'byams/ rgyal ba gang gA'i klung gi bye ma snyed/ nam mkha' rgya mtsho rol pa chen po'i snang ba chen po'i rgyud kyi rgyal po rdzogs s+ho
60 Gdm05.001 nga 1b1-12a2 byang chub kyi sems kun tu bzang po rig pa rang rtsal shar ba'i rgyud ces bya ba bo d+hi tsit+ta b+ha dra da na bi d+ya tra ni tsa ni pra tan+t+ra nA ma rdzogs so
33 Gdm05.002 nga 12a2-21b7 byang chub sems rdzogs pa chen po ye shes bdun gyi rgyud bo d+hi tsit+ta ma hA san+d+hi dz+nyA nA tan+t+ra rdzogs s+ho
59 Gdm05.003 nga 22a1-34b2 kun tu bzang po nam mkha' chen rtsa ba bsdus pa'i rgyud mA la pu tra sya ra kha sya mahA tan+t+ra kun tu bzang po nam mkha' che/ rtsa ba bsdus pa'i rgyud rdzogs s+ho// //dga' rab rdo rje ka zhus pa'o/ /man ngag rtsa ba bsdus pa'i rygud/ chos nyid mi 'gyur rgyas btab gzhag/ ban chung 'khyams po bdag gis drangs/ /bod nas rgya gar yul gyi bar/ /bka' ba bc+vo rgyas spyad pa las/ /de'i shi lnga bcu rtsa bzhi byung/ /man ngag rgyal po'i phyag du gdams/ rgya gar gyi mkhan po bdag gis drangs/ bod kyi ban+d+he bai ro tsa nas bsgyur ba'o
158 Gdm05.004 nga 34b2-45b2 rdzogs pa chen po ye shes 'khor lo gsang ba thugs rgyud zhes bya ba san+ti ma hA dz+nyA na tsakra gu h+ya tsit+ta tan+t+ra nA ma rdzogs pa chen po ye shes 'khor lo gsang ba thugs kyi rgyud zhes bya ba rdzogs s+ho
198 Gdm05.005 nga 45b2-59b5 srog gi 'byung ba rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po zhes bya ba h+ri da yo da ya ma hA tan+t+ra rA dza ma hA nA ma srog gi 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i rgyud kyi rgyal po rdzogs so/ /rgya gar gyi mkhan po gzhon nu bum pa'i zhabs kyis bsgyur ba'o// //
